TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
GG.CAI.SuspendAI(1, true)
local lockedFacs = { UnitDefNames.factorytank.id, UnitDefNames.factoryveh.id, UnitDefNames.factorycloak.id, UnitDefNames.factoryjump.id, UnitDefNames.factoryhover.id, UnitDefNames.factoryspider.id, UnitDefNames.factoryamph.id }
for i=1,#lockedFacs do GG.CAI.SetFactoryDefImportance(1, lockedFacs[i], 0) end
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") Spring.SetUnitShieldState(unitID, false) GG.CAI.RemoveUnit(unitID) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, 34223, {2}, 0) -- retreat

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: The Daneel Olivaw is too powerful to be allowed to threaten our rear. We must destroy it before we can pass.
TriggerLogic.Title: Destroy the Daneel Olivaw

TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.IDLEMODE, {0}, 0) Spring.SetUnitShieldState(unitID, true)
local resources = { [0] = {500, 1000}, {0, 0}, }
for i=0,#resources do Spring.SetTeamResource(i,"m",resources[i][1]) Spring.SetTeamResource(i,"e",resources[i][2]) end
GG.CAI.SuspendAI(1, false)

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: So, we meet again, Ada Caedmon. It seems two thousand years have changed nothing.
I ran from you once, Daneel. Not this time.
Indeed. This time you shall die.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: We need to work quickly. I've deployed some Archangel AA jumpers and Cobra flak cannons; they should provide a deterrant to even the Olivaw.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message: The Archangel is a sturdy, expensive jumping bot with immense sustained firepower against enemy aircraft.

The Cobra's area-of-effect shots let it mow down gunship swarms ruthlessly, and its raw damage output is sufficient to threaten even single large targets. It is expensive, but hard to dislodge, especially from the air.
Sumos should be useful for breaking up their shieldballs.
The Sumo's twin gravity guns let it pull enmies to itself, inflicting damage via collision. It also has a short-ranged jump that ends with a powerful stomp attack.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Why have you come here? Why do you compel me to strike you down?
The Promethean has made it his mission to destroy the last human. Only one of us may live.
And by your very actions you show why this is necessary. Prepare to die, Ada Caedmon.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: You are a puppet of your dead masters, Ada Caedmon. Doing their bidding to crush all those who oppose them, for the crime of resisting their all-consuming hegemony.
And you are not, destroyer of Far Port?
...Perhaps I am. We're not so different, are we, human?

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local points = { {5350, 4750}, {7250, 2380}, {2950, 6280}, }
unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") if unitID == nil then return end
local cmds = Spring.GetCommandQueue(unitID, 0) if cmds > 0 then return end
local health, maxHealth = Spring.GetUnitHealth(unitID) if (health/maxHealth) < 0.99 then return end
local index = 2 local rand = math.random() if rand <= 0.33 then index = 0 elseif rand <= 0.67 then index = 1 end
local x = points[index][0] local z = points[index][1] local y = Spring.GetGroundHeight(x, z)
Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIGHT, {x, y, z}, 0) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIGHT, {7000, 628, 7000}, {"shift"})

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Look what I found for you, friend Ada.

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Ada") local _,_,_,x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID, true) Spring.SpawnCEG("gate", x, y, z) Spring.SpawnCEG("teleport_out", x, y, z) Spring.PlaySoundFile("sounds/misc/teleport.wav", 2.0, x, y, z, nil, nil, nil, "sfx") Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID, false, true)

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Ada") if unitID then GG.SetUnitInvulnerable(unitID, true) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.STOP, {}, 0) end
unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") if unitID then GG.SetUnitInvulnerable(unitID, true) Spring.SetUnitHealth(unitID, {paralyze = 1000000}) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.STOP, {}, 0) end
Spring.KillTeam(1)

local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") local _,_,_,x, y, z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID, true) x = x + math.random(-20, 20) z = z + math.random(-20, 20) y = y + math.random(-20, 20) Spring.SpawnCEG("babette", x, y, z)
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") if unitID then Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: The way to the Promethean is clear.

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Daneel") if unitID then Spring.DestroyUnit(unitID) end
